{"tid":685743,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[快閃]4日4夜東京爆肝爆肚玩命之旅","createTime":"2018-05-31T16:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T10:43:00.000Z","uid":18394,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"5cc4a3088f87a2dcf5fa6243eae2c4c3bfe12ebe","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:01:43.000Z","msg":"Halo 又係我阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩完左個日本遊記又黎寫新一篇遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次目的地係東京！<br />\n<br />\n點解係玩命之旅呢 你睇落去咪知lor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又黎戴頭盔時間 呢篇遊記影既相同文筆唔係特別好  請大家多多見諒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次篇遊記主要係以食為主所以景點就冇乜lu 如果想睇景點既巴絲真係唔好意思啦 但如果你想知東京有咩食的話 呢度一定幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為今個trip 最高峰係可以一日食五餐正餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單介紹下行程先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDay1 夜機到東京 大江戶溫泉<br />\nDay2 上野 涉谷 原宿 新宿<br />\nDay3 築地 富士急 目黑<br />\nDay4 下谷 秋葉原 池袋 夜機回港"},{"pid":"14f06bf6afb75b29e98c97a5178e252a5fe16cca","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:01:54.000Z","msg":"即刻黎講下day 1先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n作為一個專業冗員 請左半日假就飛去機場搭飛機去旅行lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235053_32a13ae1a931b95ffcc1457bb72836a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235053_32a13ae1a931b95ffcc1457bb72836a4.png&h=5c44d31e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n窮撚今次又係搭UO 垃圾UO 又delay<br />\n今次delay 真係比佢搞死 因為深夜由羽田去大江戶溫泉既巴士得一班 miss 左就要轉去平和溫泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235124_ff99c187c3e5f310396fa57e87dfbf47.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235124_ff99c187c3e5f310396fa57e87dfbf47.png&h=a7001ff7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好好彩 一落機幾乎以跑既速度跑去過關 終於趕得切買去大江戶既車飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235153_23aac4ddbb75245f58142adcd525a8fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235153_23aac4ddbb75245f58142adcd525a8fb.png&h=88d6ca8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚我地就冇book 酒店 係大江戶休息室瞓就算 不過休息室其實幾嘈 又有人打機 又有鼻寒聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235210_a81623990f3180c0fa871bb3cb0386c2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235210_a81623990f3180c0fa871bb3cb0386c2.png&h=e9b14205&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為太肚餓 又因為太夜d 餐廳已經收哂就去買左呢d 叮叮食品 我就買左個小丸子食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235232_91ffd12fdf99628da5133b35a3db1de9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235232_91ffd12fdf99628da5133b35a3db1de9.png&h=855f8aac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n睇個樣就知好唔好食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235249_3cac37e5591070c81acf2fc39b50156a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235249_3cac37e5591070c81acf2fc39b50156a.png&h=e7afc573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n浸完溫泉最好就係飲牛奶啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/31/235313_ba80b9af774e366fd308c6dd0bb451ae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F31%2F235313_ba80b9af774e366fd308c6dd0bb451ae.png&h=9591e5f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係休息室真係好難瞓得著 不過因為太攰既關係我都瞓左3~4個鐘<br />\n之後就再去浸多次溫泉 就出發第2日既行程啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"446ec2b8b1f931ccfec997737166248095e00e75","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:04:44.000Z","msg":"今晚係咁多先 唔夠喉可以睇住我上篇遊記先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次遊記因為日數太短 我驚好快完 所以盡量慢慢打 打多少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家記得留名阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2a51e00ff58472d722163dd1a482aa9a2fa685","tid":685743,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:06:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"9096cbe18345da009e4c67f67eb74f46185a2e84","tid":685743,"uid":69302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"5f0760d7a1855d35120146d4a980ec929d860fe5","tid":685743,"uid":80533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:17:50.000Z","msg":"留名j手睇美食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab785724a0aae2c89913e337833e2878f007824","tid":685743,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:17:55.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"ecff7e01a0040f2d29f0a10e6dd66d430de0ae22","tid":685743,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571fdf53216a3b53f288478f9d439be21a3bd287","tid":685743,"uid":30694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a6b7be9b8b050a9ead064a52381f32f4fd9843","tid":685743,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:33:24.000Z","msg":"正 遲 d 第一次去東京參考下"},{"pid":"97e7f7a865a6f8acf3e46fd388fa0bff30ce04d3","tid":685743,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:43:05.000Z","msg":"有靚手睇有無靚腳睇?"},{"pid":"20f30b03173c0ae31dcc1668d90a5703dcbb1b95","tid":685743,"uid":27728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:48:31.000Z","msg":"成個旅程用幾錢到？"},{"pid":"00e03c43bb86e885ce3cb86ed143149793826c8a","tid":685743,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:28:31.000Z","msg":"行程都ok呀唔算太多地方"},{"pid":"978f2251bb6ed14b7e8dd55cc1e4b0b5b4b4c762","tid":685743,"uid":59804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T00:50:51.000Z","msg":"4日4夜都算快閃?"},{"pid":"781f41bca0e35d7e4bbb78d45c4c4d1f4c0b534e","tid":685743,"uid":23511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T02:38:37.000Z","msg":"係大江戶食過個拉麵好難食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16743eb444d5b195646dacd5a7ec79e3511f18a6","tid":685743,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:45:36.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d413eadb69874ebcc46644dfa723928b121e579","tid":685743,"uid":145494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇得去日本 睇下樓主呢個遊記都好"},{"pid":"bfade1fd63a15e94037e65280ea82ea387c9d201","tid":685743,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"0e1e2569f5d6cb541f3757d1d3cf2f819cf8c86a","tid":685743,"uid":150230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:27:04.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b1567d78671895a28fa0da6f77a635a2efb1ded6","tid":685743,"uid":84921,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:24:34.000Z","msg":"繼續支持拉面，夾公仔之旅"},{"pid":"2db5cbf82514b542ff36b0f7ffb35776d21b4eab","tid":685743,"uid":36279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T09:33:20.000Z","msg":"留名J樓主隻手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c233f43773e38f3aa280747b40f7d6db54b88b62","tid":685743,"uid":44405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:08:33.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"04defeb05ff5a6eb704d53f8abd5171f74c279b7","tid":685743,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T12:24:50.000Z","msg":"留名等J腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1146e3db7f73147941d72894512c288fed12954c","tid":685743,"uid":136299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T13:39:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebd4ede6b34b51e205a0640abb032978a8cab9f","tid":685743,"uid":36065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:17:40.000Z","msg":"我都諗住9月 10月 4日3夜 東京食野 不過可能到時係搭凌晨機去"},{"pid":"c755038d4f0d3fb39a04f89053e4593be6f86bbb","tid":685743,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"又睇到日本遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24d5f57c5cd875de66fb106fb748fb2a2c2a5894","tid":685743,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfade1fd63a15e94037e65280ea82ea387c9d201","tid":685743,"uid":42344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:52:14.000Z","msg":"留名"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T18:26:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57f9e124c13c65cf6876fa54e1f1d29fe9f43965","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:26:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"> 你地唔好咁痴線啦 男人手都J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nBtw 黎到Day 2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次住既酒店係位於秋葉原既維亞酒店 點解會簡住係秋葉原<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我地係毒撚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為未夠鐘check in 所以我地就係酒店放低行李再出發啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎緊呢幾日都係住呢度啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/150658_23aad83d8240dcccd1efe62d2beef585.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F150658_23aad83d8240dcccd1efe62d2beef585.png&h=e06e0de7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一站我地就去左上野既阿美橫町去食lunch 啦<br />\n第一餐 食鰻魚飯！！<br />\n我地食呢間就係應該大家都識既 平價鰻魚飯 名代 宇奈とと 啦！<br />\n點解會食呢間？事關我係大阪天神橋都食過呢間既分店 但當時食係覺得d 鰻魚好腥唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n家母就話佢係東京上野分店食過勁好食 同呢間完全唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係因為咁 就試下上野分店同大阪既係咪咁唔同先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n叫左個鰻魚玉子燒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正正常常 無伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/145628_a88421dc57235b449f836caf10e58217.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F145628_a88421dc57235b449f836caf10e58217.png&h=d897b9c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲有呢個價值500yen 既鰻魚飯 咁平既價錢 邊度搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢真係比我係大阪食個時冇咁腥 但都有少少魚腥味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得唔算係一個好食既鰻魚飯 但佢係對得住個價錢 500yen 一個飯 唔難食 仲要食得飽 冇乜筆直既朋友 而對鰻魚飯要求唔高既可以一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/145637_088cc73e8b430237171a17b752d43c12.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F145637_088cc73e8b430237171a17b752d43c12.png&h=428038d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"> <strong>鰻魚飯店家資料：<br />\n名代  宇奈とと鰻魚飯(上野店)<br />\n地址：東京都台東区上野6-11-15 </span></strong><br />\n<br />\n之後就去食肉の大山 <br />\n呢間鋪頭人流好多 相信都幾出名（因為係友人話呢間好食 所以我唔知間野係咪好出名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n呢度最出名就係炸牛肉餅 當然要食返個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個肉餅係好重牛同洋蔥既味道 新鮮炸起所以熱辣辣同流哂肉汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得咁多人排隊黎食 咁當然佢呢度仲有其他炸物買既 不過我就冇試到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/145700_9f1bbbdc6364252c7692801ddbb2ceb7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F145700_9f1bbbdc6364252c7692801ddbb2ceb7.png&h=638306ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>店家資料：<br />\n肉の大山<br />\n地址: 東京都台東区上野6-13-2<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後再係阿美橫町買左2串生果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係士多啤梨阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿美橫町好多呢d 一串串切好左既生果賣 懶得去超市而又想試下日本生果既話就可以係度買少少黎食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/145722_4e486e38c4d2b84b3aa69be8b1d4d32b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F145722_4e486e38c4d2b84b3aa69be8b1d4d32b.png&h=7b55507a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去完上野我地就趕去下個目的地lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45c257b4b84e1b64d32c562771cc4745f0bb3ce4","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"97e7f7a865a6f8acf3e46fd388fa0bff30ce04d3","tid":685743,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:43:05.000Z","msg":"有靚手睇有無靚腳睇?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/152739_cb3d99b3301abc0f3f8fa7c1edc17e19.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F152739_cb3d99b3301abc0f3f8fa7c1edc17e19.png&h=bf6b05d8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2ed190925b9cf0e227ef9e3bcd3ea26e8a8cee2a","tid":685743,"uid":18394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20f30b03173c0ae31dcc1668d90a5703dcbb1b95","tid":685743,"uid":27728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-31T22:48:31.000Z","msg":"成個旅程用幾錢到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T07:28:23.000Z","msg":"sorry 巴打呢個真係唔係好記得<img src=